#Steps: 

Install Docker 

Install Wazuh using docker-compose 

Open Ports 

Docker Images Required: 

wazuh/wazuh-manager 

wazuh/wazuh-indexer 

wazuh/wazuh-dashboard 

All these Wazuh Docker images are found in the Docker hub. 

#Install Docker 

To install docker on ubuntu 

Remove old config and docker installation 

sudo apt-get remove docker docker-engine docker.io 

Update the system 

sudo apt update 

Install the docker 

sudo apt install docker.io 

Confirm docker is installed properly 

sudo docker --version 
